subject: Re: [Read_Alphabet] Read's Original Manual
msgSnippet: Hi Moira, Yes, it s there under Files  Resources. There are two versions, the original: QuikScriptManual(Image).pdf (and also QuikScriptManual.djvu ) and
messageBody:
Hi Moira,

Yes, it's there under Files > Resources. There are two versions, the original: 'QuikScriptManual(Image).pdf' (and also 'QuikScriptManual.djvu') and an incomplete transcription: 'qs manual modern (beta).pdf'

Ted


On 10/5/07, Moira O'Brien <mj@...> wrote:

I was looking in the files section to see if there was a copy of the
original Quikscript manual but was unable to find it.

Is it there? If not, I have a couple of copies and will scan and
upload them.

regards

Moira
